Source: e2fsprogs
Section: admin
Priority: required
Maintainer: Tux Mason <tuxmason@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9), util-linux-dev
Standards-Version: 3.9.5
Homepage: http://e2fsprogs.sourceforge.net/

Package: e2fsprogs
Section: admin
Priority: required
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: libc (>= 1.1.8), ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: utilities for managing ext2, ext3, and ext4 filesystems
 E2fsprogs is a collection of utilities for managing ext2, ext3, and ext4
 filesystems.
 .
 This package also provides the shared libraries libcom_err, libss, libe2p,
 and libext2fs.

Package: e2fsprogs-dev
Section: libdevel
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: libc-dev, util-linux-dev, e2fsprogs (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Development headers and static libraries for e2fsprogs
 This package provides pkgconfig data and header files required for
 development using e2fsprogs.
 .
 Also included are the static libraries libcom_err, libss, libe2p,
 and libext2fs.

Package: e2fsprogs-doc
Section: doc
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Recommends: man-db, info, e2fsprogs (= ${binary:Version})
Description: documentation for e2fsprogs
 This package provides info and man pages for utilities provided by e2fsprogs.
